function NewTarifs() {
setCardName(e.target.value)} maxLength="30" placeholder="Nom sur la carte" required />
setCardNumber(e.target.value)} maxLength="19" placeholder="XXXX XXXX XXXX XXXX" required />
setCardDate(e.target.value)} placeholder="MM/AA" required />
setCardCode(e.target.value)} maxLength="3" placeholder="CVC" required />
} export default NewTarifs;
